column428:
If order has items that have been shipped (at least 1 item with tracking number), then:
  1. tracking list header should read 'Your Shipments';
  2. there should be no subtitle copy following under the tracking header;

Else 
  1.  tracking list header should read 'We've Received Your Order';
  2. there should be subtitle copy following under the tracking header that reads  `You will receive an email when your tracking information becomes available. This page will also update with your status.`;

